**who —** HYRULE — the eighth lineage — the third game-world

**what —** The Legend of Zelda — the eternal cycle of Link, Zelda, and Ganon; the Triforce of Power, Wisdom, and Courage; the Master Sword and the kingdom of Hyrule.

