**why —** Three goddesses left a relic of pure wish, and bound a hero, a princess, and a demon to refight for it across every age.

**how —** Crystallized from The Legend of Zelda — the whole saga, distilled to canon.

**◌ the mythos —** Three goddesses left a relic of pure wish, and bound a hero, a princess, and a demon to refight for it across every age. One legend, retold across forty years and three timelines — and always, courage draws the blade.

